text: Rita de Luna (born 1 September 1929) is a Guatemalan equestrian. She competed in the individual eventing at the 1976 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1929 births Category:Living people Category:Guatemalan female equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Guatemala Category:Equestrians at the 1976 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
